<br>
As far as Rezz's go, I have never been in a position to need to pay for one for myself. If there is no cleric in my group, then I suck it up, and take the loss of experience. I have however procured services for fellow players, and paid with sow potions. The clerics can really use them, and I think are a different type of compensation from the norm. <br>
<br>
